rComments: cara taught me at smu-halifax.  she's really nice and always willing to help.  her class is difficult and a bit abstract but i learned alot.  and she covers stuff like hockey and the history of the donut which is cool.
Cara's a new teacher and it shows.  She's enthusiastic and full of fun ideas and loves her job. So many profs that I encounter are past their prime! And she's hot, which is a bonus.

Prof. Spittal is a new lecturer and so struggled with the material at first.  But once she found her footing we all got into it.  I loved the stuff we did on hockey and pop culture and the trip to the Maritime  Museum.
